This paper is about designing an online question answering system that balances effectiveness and efficiency. The paper proposes a novel deep cascade learning model for multi-document reading comprehension. The paper involves natural language processing, machine learning, and information retrieval techniques, which are typically covered in the arXiv CS sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and computer vision (cs.CV).
